  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 200°C.",
    "In a large skillet, caramelize the lardons-render over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion to the skillet and cook until softened.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix together the clear honey, sour cream, and paprika.",
    "Combine the flour and breadcrumbs in another bowl.",
    "Add the honey mixture to the skillet and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Sprinkle the flour mixture over the top of the skillet contents.",
    "Transfer the skillet to the preheated oven and cook for 20 minutes.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for 5 minutes before serving."
